Absolutely amazing, Love this game since the day I got it. The amount of secrets and subtle easter eggs are mind blowing. Only downside is, it doesn't have much replay value. Admittedly you do get quite a few hours out of it through the first play through but after the first 2-3 times you complete every ending, it gets quite boring but after not playing it for months and coming back to it, its fun re-figuring out all the secrets. Definitely worth the money if you like puzzles and easter eggs.
